data.description: Discover your dream home! This 3 bed, 2.5 bath gem boasts the ultimate in entertainment and luxury. The garage has been transformed into a state-of-the-art man cave with a theater room, working bar, fireplace, and a fitness center. Plus, a bedroom turned into a walk-in closet fit for a king or queen! Even better, $30,000 worth of top-notch furniture and appliances are included. Don't miss out on this one-of-a-kind opportunity to live the good life!
